The Association Code of Law
Statute 0000
The oath of the Associate is a life bond. There shall be no exit
from the Association without the spilling of blood.
The Associate in question may only earn their departure in a duel
to the death.

This is the account of Athena Agard.

Fight practice!!! I had da best time making violence and learning from this awesome team. Thank you @stevebrownwrestler for everything, as always.🦆🙏🏼
And thank you to @garrettxwarren, @bdonski, @kevindorman, @derekpueblo, @tuhhny_vee, @aarontoney, @waynedalglish, @nathanhaugaard, and @tempestfreerunning for your time, knowledge, and energy. I’m so grateful. 🙏🏼🥰

But really, what is “it”??

There has to be a switch. We train this extensively at the gym. You have to have the ability to turn it on, but also turn it right back off. And sometimes dance. 😎💃🏻 #SomosLobos #Chau #GameFace #Boxing 🎥 - @sweetsciencefilms

I wanted to… so I did!

Try something new, why the fuck not?

I did none of this alone. This is the work of a team! 🐺
This wouldn’t be possible without:

THE BEST Coach, @eddiearrazola. I am so fortunate for the extremely generous amounts of knowledge, time, and support you have gifted me. I am forever grateful for you and everything you do. You’re the best. 

THE BEST gym, @lobosboxingclub. The teammates and community are unmatched. #somoslobos 

THE BEST hand-holder/teammate @cregansollers. I am so thankful that you have been with me every step of the way and for punching me hard.

Thank you @team_navarro_boxing @eddieherediaboxingclub for putting on an awesome show and being in my corner. 

Thank you @the.elitesmith for getting our whole team ready!! 

Thank you @timothy.kwon @sweetsciencefilms @lorenshin for capturing the goodness!

Thankful for you guys @lorenshin @goodmorningfreedom @laurena22 @nikkihru @stephen_opsal thank you for the support! 

AND THANK YOU TO EVERYONE WHO CAME AND WATCHED! It means the world, I am so appreciative.

Lieutenant Suna Jensu 🫡

@starwars @ahsokaofficial @dave.filoni @jonfavreau 

This was so much fun!! I am so grateful. Thank you @dave.filoni @jonfavreau @jjdashnaw @ocs_leonard @nat_pad @sunmoonl for the opportunities and trust!!🙏🏼
